  NULL,
  'Unknown, Data Deficient',
  NULL,
  '{"other_names": "", "meristics": "Dorsal spines: 3; Dorsal soft rays: 19-20; Anal spines: 0; Anal soft rays: 15-17.", "appearance": "Preserved specimens dark brown and mottled with lighter brown, smaller specimens with irregular cross bars.", "about": "It is only found in the Southeast Atlantic and western Indian Ocean from South Africa, from Durban to Port St. Johns, Transkei. The depth range is not known. This species is demersal and prefers tropical waters", "biology": "Max length: 29.0 cm TL", "citation": "FishBase, Wikipedia, The IUCN Red List of Threatened Species"}',
